<p>Aloha guys! Here's my first attempt at an SCP. It's filled with 3,071 words. I know it definitely needs work, but because I'm basically blind, I'm sure whoever stumbles upon this can easily correct my mistakes faster.<br />
So, have at it: <a href="http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/drcope">http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/drcope</a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13894429/the-friendly-shadow#post-4835770">Greenlights in the replies.</a></p>
<p>Brief Intro: It's a living shadow attached to a human (Clarence).</p>
<p>I believe I must certainly work on the Interviews. Other than that, I'm not observant or educated enough to see what else needs corrected. To anyone about to Crit this, thanks. I always need help.</p>

