															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doggol" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6991250); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6991250&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610251592" alt="Doggol" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6991250)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doggol" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6991250); return false;" >Doggol</a></span> <span class="odate time_1608725338 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">23 Dec 2020 12:08</span>
														</div>
