<p>Yeah, that's fine. Go at your own pace - I apologise if I was overloading you with feedback. About the collapsible within collapsible, as far as I know, it would only work with wikidot bootstrap (as said in <a href="http://community.wikidot.com/forum/t-1065728/collapsible-within-collapsible">this discussion thread</a>). I'm no coding expert, so To get around this I would probably make a div with the text 'level three clearance required, please input credentials - similar to what they have going on in <a href="/scp-2316">SCP-2316</a></p>
